metadata.name: Dummy Boy Gold
metadata.description:
Own a limited collectors piece of NFT music history from 6ix9ine's debut Billboard charting album. This gold framed piece of art, limited to 125 pieces, integrates the second single "Fefe" feat Nicki Minaj from his platinum selling Dummy Boy album.

2 random Gold NFT buyers will be selected to go on Instagram Live with @6ix9ine and receive a merchandise package
